    All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.interfaces.ClientRequest, edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.interfaces.Request, edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.interfaces.RequestIdentifier, ExtensiblePacketInterface, PacketInterface

    public class SelectRequestPacket<NodeIDType>
extends BasicPacketWithNs<NodeIDType>
implements edu.umass.cs.gigapaxos.interfaces.ClientRequest
    A SelectRequestPacket is like a DNS_SUBTYPE_QUERY packet without a GUID, but with a key and value. The semantics is that we want to look up all the records that have a field named key with the given value. We also use this to do automatic group GUID maintenence.
    Author:
    westy
